paragraphs.title: create RESULTS for CLUSTERING, #1
paragraphs.text:
%script

create table OML_CLUSTERING_RES_WA1
as select
        OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA1."ID" as "ID",
        replace(regexp_substr(OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA1."ID", '[^+]+', 1, 1),'-',' ') as "CUSTOMER",
        regexp_substr(OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA1."ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1) as "PRODUCT GROUP",
        OML_TRANSACTIONS_WA1."DIFV TODATE" as "DIFV TODATE",
        OML_TRANSACTIONS_WA1."DIFV LAST6M" as "DIFV LAST6M",
        OML_TRANSACTIONS_WA1."DIFV LAST1M" as "DIFV LAST1M",
        case greatest("CLUSTER 6","CLUSTER 7","CLUSTER 9","CLUSTER 10","CLUSTER 11","CLUSTER 13","CLUSTER 15","CLUSTER 16","CLUSTER 17") 
            when "CLUSTER 6" then 'A' when "CLUSTER 7" then 'B' when "CLUSTER 9" then 'C' 
            when "CLUSTER 10" then 'D' when "CLUSTER 11" then 'E' when "CLUSTER 13" then 'F' 
            when "CLUSTER 15" then 'G' when "CLUSTER 16" then 'H' when "CLUSTER 17" then 'I' end as "CLUSTER",
        greatest("CLUSTER 6","CLUSTER 7","CLUSTER 9","CLUSTER 10","CLUSTER 11","CLUSTER 13","CLUSTER 15","CLUSTER 16","CLUSTER 17") as "PROBABILITY"
    from
        OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA1
    join
        OML_TRANSACTIONS_WA1 on OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA1."ID"=OML_TRANSACTIONS_WA1."ID";

paragraphs.title: view RESULTS for CLUSTERING, #1, CLUSTERS, detailed
paragraphs.text:
%sql

select
    "CLUSTER" as "CLUSTER",
    cast(min("DIFV TODATE") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFV TODATE MIN",
    cast(avg("DIFV TODATE") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFV TODATE AVG",
    cast(max("DIFV TODATE") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFV TODATE MAX",
    cast(min("DIFV LAST6M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFV LAST6M MIN",
    cast(avg("DIFV LAST6M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFV LAST6M AVG",
    cast(max("DIFV LAST6M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFV LAST6M MAX",
    cast(min("DIFV LAST1M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFV LAST1M MIN",
    cast(avg("DIFV LAST1M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFV LAST1M AVG",
    cast(max("DIFV LAST1M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFV LAST1M MAX"
from
    OML_CLUSTERING_RES_WA1
group by
    "CLUSTER"
order by
    cast(avg("DIFV TODATE") as numeric(6,2)),
    cast(avg("DIFV LAST6M") as numeric(6,2)),
    cast(avg("DIFV LAST1M") as numeric(6,2));

paragraphs.title: view RESULTS for CLUSTERING, #1, PRODUCT GROUP
paragraphs.text:
%sql

select
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1) as "PRODUCT GROUP",
    count("ID") as "CUSTOMERS",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 6") as numeric(6,2)) as "CLUSTER A",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 7") as numeric(6,2)) as "CLUSTER B",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 9") as numeric(6,2)) as "CLUSTER C",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 10") as numeric(6,2)) as "CLUSTER D",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 11") as numeric(6,2)) as "CLUSTER E",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 13") as numeric(6,2)) as "CLUSTER F",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 15") as numeric(6,2)) as "CLUSTER G",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 16") as numeric(6,2)) as "CLUSTER H",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 17") as numeric(6,2)) as "CLUSTER I"
from
    OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA1
group by
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1)
order by
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1);

%sql

select
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1) as "PRODUCT GROUP",
    case when avg("CLUSTER 6")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 6"),avg("CLUSTER 7"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 10"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 13"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER A'
         when avg("CLUSTER 7")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 6"),avg("CLUSTER 7"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 10"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 13"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER B'
         when avg("CLUSTER 9")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 6"),avg("CLUSTER 7"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 10"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 13"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER C'
         when avg("CLUSTER 10")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 6"),avg("CLUSTER 7"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 10"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 13"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER D'
         when avg("CLUSTER 11")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 6"),avg("CLUSTER 7"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 10"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 13"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER E'
         when avg("CLUSTER 13")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 6"),avg("CLUSTER 7"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 10"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 13"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER F'
         when avg("CLUSTER 15")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 6"),avg("CLUSTER 7"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 10"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 13"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER G'
         when avg("CLUSTER 16")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 6"),avg("CLUSTER 7"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 10"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 13"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER H'
         when avg("CLUSTER 17")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 6"),avg("CLUSTER 7"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 10"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 13"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER I'
         end as "CLUSTER"
from
    OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA1

    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1)

    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1);

paragraphs.title: create RESULTS for CLUSTERING, #2
paragraphs.text:
%script

create table OML_CLUSTERING_RES_WA2
as select
        OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA2."ID" as "ID",
        replace(regexp_substr(OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA2."ID", '[^+]+', 1, 1),'-',' ') as "CUSTOMER",
        regexp_substr(OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA2."ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1) as "PRODUCT GROUP",
        OML_TRANSACTIONS_WA2."DIFP TODATE" as "DIFP TODATE",
        OML_TRANSACTIONS_WA2."DIFP LAST6M" as "DIFP LAST6M",
        OML_TRANSACTIONS_WA2."DIFP LAST1M" as "DIFP LAST1M",
        case greatest("CLUSTER 5","CLUSTER 8","CLUSTER 9","CLUSTER 11","CLUSTER 12","CLUSTER 14","CLUSTER 15","CLUSTER 16","CLUSTER 17") 
            when "CLUSTER 5" then 'A' when "CLUSTER 8" then 'B' when "CLUSTER 9" then 'C' 
            when "CLUSTER 11" then 'D' when "CLUSTER 12" then 'E' when "CLUSTER 14" then 'F' 
            when "CLUSTER 15" then 'G' when "CLUSTER 16" then 'H' when "CLUSTER 17" then 'I' end as "CLUSTER",
        greatest("CLUSTER 5","CLUSTER 8","CLUSTER 9","CLUSTER 11","CLUSTER 12","CLUSTER 14","CLUSTER 15","CLUSTER 16","CLUSTER 17") as "PROBABILITY"
    from
        OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA2
    join
        OML_TRANSACTIONS_WA2 on OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA2."ID"=OML_TRANSACTIONS_WA2."ID";

paragraphs.title: view RESULTS for CLUSTERING, #2, CLUSTERS, detailed
paragraphs.text:
%sql

select
    "CLUSTER" as "CLUSTER",
    cast(min("DIFP TODATE") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFP TODATE MIN",
    cast(avg("DIFP TODATE") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFP TODATE AVG",
    cast(max("DIFP TODATE") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFP TODATE MAX",
    cast(min("DIFP LAST6M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFP LAST6M MIN",
    cast(avg("DIFP LAST6M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFP LAST6M AVG",
    cast(max("DIFP LAST6M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFP LAST6M MAX",
    cast(min("DIFP LAST1M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFP LAST1M MIN",
    cast(avg("DIFP LAST1M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFP LAST1M AVG",
    cast(max("DIFP LAST1M") as numeric(6,2)) as "DIFP LAST1M MAX"
from
    OML_CLUSTERING_RES_WA2
group by
    "CLUSTER"
order by
    cast(avg("DIFP TODATE") as numeric(6,2)),
    cast(avg("DIFP LAST6M") as numeric(6,2)),
    cast(avg("DIFP LAST1M") as numeric(6,2));

paragraphs.title: view RESULTS for CLUSTERING, #2, PRODUCT GROUP
paragraphs.text:
%sql

select
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1) as "PRODUCT GROUP",
    count("ID") as "CUSTOMERS",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 5") as numeric(6,2)) as "AVG C5",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 8") as numeric(6,2)) as "AVG C8",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 9") as numeric(6,2)) as "AVG C9",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 11") as numeric(6,2)) as "AVG C11",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 12") as numeric(6,2)) as "AVG C12",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 14") as numeric(6,2)) as "AVG C14",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 15") as numeric(6,2)) as "AVG C15",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 16") as numeric(6,2)) as "AVG C16",
    cast(avg("CLUSTER 17") as numeric(6,2)) as "AVG C17"
from
    OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA2
group by
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1)
order by
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1);

paragraphs.title: view RESULTS for CLUSTERING, #2, PRODUCT GROUP
paragraphs.text:
%sql

select
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1) as "PRODUCT GROUP",
    case when avg("CLUSTER 5")>15 then 'X' else '' end as "CLUSTER A",
    case when avg("CLUSTER 8")>15 then 'X' else '' end as "CLUSTER B",
    case when avg("CLUSTER 9")>15 then 'X' else '' end as "CLUSTER C",
    case when avg("CLUSTER 11")>15 then 'X' else '' end as "CLUSTER D",
    case when avg("CLUSTER 12")>15 then 'X' else '' end as "CLUSTER E",
    case when avg("CLUSTER 14")>15 then 'X' else '' end as "CLUSTER F",
    case when avg("CLUSTER 15")>15 then 'X' else '' end as "CLUSTER G",
    case when avg("CLUSTER 16")>15 then 'X' else '' end as "CLUSTER H",
    case when avg("CLUSTER 17")>15 then 'X' else '' end as "CLUSTER I"
from
    OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA2
group by
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1)
order by
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1);

paragraphs.title: , short
paragraphs.text:
%sql

select
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1) as "PRODUCT GROUP",
    case when avg("CLUSTER 5")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 5"),avg("CLUSTER 8"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 12"),avg("CLUSTER 14"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER A'
         when avg("CLUSTER 8")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 5"),avg("CLUSTER 8"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 12"),avg("CLUSTER 14"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER B'
         when avg("CLUSTER 9")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 5"),avg("CLUSTER 8"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 12"),avg("CLUSTER 14"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER C'
         when avg("CLUSTER 11")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 5"),avg("CLUSTER 8"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 12"),avg("CLUSTER 14"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER D'
         when avg("CLUSTER 12")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 5"),avg("CLUSTER 8"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 12"),avg("CLUSTER 14"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER E'
         when avg("CLUSTER 14")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 5"),avg("CLUSTER 8"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 12"),avg("CLUSTER 14"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER F'
         when avg("CLUSTER 15")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 5"),avg("CLUSTER 8"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 12"),avg("CLUSTER 14"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER G'
         when avg("CLUSTER 16")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 5"),avg("CLUSTER 8"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 12"),avg("CLUSTER 14"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER H'
         when avg("CLUSTER 17")=greatest(avg("CLUSTER 5"),avg("CLUSTER 8"),avg("CLUSTER 9"),avg("CLUSTER 11"),avg("CLUSTER 12"),avg("CLUSTER 14"),avg("CLUSTER 15"),avg("CLUSTER 16"),avg("CLUSTER 17")) then 'CLUSTER I'
         end as "CLUSTER"
from
    OML_CLUSTERING_PRD_WA2
group by
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1)
order by
    regexp_substr("ID", '[^+]+$', 1, 1);
